@startuml UC-AUTH-01
left to right direction
actor Customer
actor "AI Agent (verification)" as AI_Agent
actor "Security / Ops Team" as Ops
rectangle "iNB System" {
  usecase "Attempt Login" as UC_Login
  usecase "Automated Identity Verification" as UC_AIVerify
  usecase "Manual Re-activation / Investigation" as UC_ManualUnlock
}
Customer --> UC_Login
UC_Login --> UC_AIVerify
AI_Agent --> UC_AIVerify
UC_AIVerify .> UC_ManualUnlock : escalate if unresolved
Ops --> UC_ManualUnlock
UC_ManualUnlock --> Customer
@enduml
